                        About
                    </h2>
                    <p>Welcome to the professional webpage of Subhajit Ghosh, a dedicated researcher in computational biology. With over five years experience, his focus spans network biology, transcriptomics, and machine learning to uncover new biomarkers and therapeutic insights for complex diseases including hepatocellular carcinoma, PCOS, and rheumatoid arthritis.</p>
                    <p>Expertise in statistical analysis, molecular docking, molecular dynamics, and advanced Python/R scripting for genomics and clinical data interpretation.</p>
